Detailed Description

cvmx_mdbw::_mem_dbe_int

This register set, specifies the double-bit error status for all memories; where a value 0 = pass or never run and 1 = fail per MDBW. These generate fatal error interrupts to the PSM, which drives this signal to the CIU.
